headline.main: DEATH OF FRED DOUGLASS; The Negro Leader Dies Suddenly in His Own Hallway. APPARENTLY IN PERFECT HEALTH He Attended the Convention of the Women's National Council and Was to Have Spoken Last Night. DEATH OF FRED DOUGLAS

snippet: WASHINGTON, Feb. 20. -- Frederick Douglass dropped dead in the hallway of his residence on Anacostia Heights this evening at 7 o'clock. He had been in the highest spirits, and apparently in the best of health, despite his seventy-eight years, when...
